  "claim_boundary": "Result-sink and fanout smoke is local and scoped; local Vortex output/fanout is feature-gated and flat-scalar only. Replay/fidelity proof, S3/object-store write, table commits, broad Vortex writer behavior, and production sink support remain planned or blocked.",
  "runnable_example": "ctx.read_csv(\"target/input.csv\").select(\"id\").limit(10).fanout({\"jsonl\": \"target/out.jsonl\", \"csv\": \"target/out.csv\"}, allow_overwrite=True); # with --features vortex-write: ctx.read_csv(\"target/input.csv\").select(\"id\").limit(10).write_vortex(\"target/out.vortex\", allow_overwrite=True)",
  "expected_output_evidence": "A local result-sink or fanout proof artifact with per-output digest/certificate fields for admitted local sinks; Vortex rows include artifact digest and upstream writer/reopen proof when built with --features vortex-write. Full replay/fidelity evidence only lands after later OutputPlan slices.",
